DestroyFunc journalctlattach
AddToFunc journalctlattach
+ I Exec `exec $[TERMINAL] -geometry 170x50+100+40 -name Journalctl -e tmux new-session -A -s journalctl "journalctl -b -f -n 1000"`

DestroyFunc scrollandmove
AddToFunc scrollandmove
+ I Scroll $0 $1
+ I Move w$0 w$1 ewmhiwa

DestroyFunc switchpageandrefocus
AddToFunc switchpageandrefocus
+ I GotoPage $0 $1
+ I All (CurrentPage, Focused, !Iconic) FlipFocus NoWarp
+ I TestRc (NoMatch) Prev (CurrentPage, AcceptsFocus, !Iconic) FlipFocus NoWarp

